    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>You blow into your open hand, and a fire forms in your palm. You can hold the fire or throw it at a creature.</em></p><p><strong>Utility Spell</strong> </p><p>A flame appears in your empty hand and harms neither you nor your equipment. The flame sheds bright light in a 10-foot radius and dim light for an additional 10 feet.</p><p>You can also attack with the flame, which extinguishes it, either when you cast this spell, or later as an action.</p><p><strong>Ranged Spell Attack</strong> </p><p>If this spell damages a vehicle or object that is flammable and has hit points, the object is set on fire**.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Hit:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 1d8 fire]] damage*</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*At Higher Levels:</strong> This spell's damage increases by 1d8 when you reach a total character or creature level of 5th level ([[/damage 2d8 fire]]), 11th level ([[/damage 3d8 fire]]), and 17th level ([[/damage 4d8 fire]]).</p><p><em>**Some objects may be too large or flammable to be simply extinguished as an action, and will require creative solutions. Additionally, some vehicles or other objects may have a 'damage threshold'. For example, a fire bolt would have to deal at least 5 damage to damage and ignite a wooden catapult. Once ignited, the ignited object takes [[/damage 1d10 fire]] damage at the end of each of the caster's turns, which is dealt regardless of the target's damage threshold.</em></p>",
            "chat": "<strong>Utility Spell</strong> </p><p>A flame appears in your empty hand and harms neither you nor your equipment. The flame sheds bright light in a 10-foot radius and dim light for an additional 10 feet.</p><p>You can also attack with the flame, which extinguishes it, either when you cast this spell, or later as an action.</p><p><strong>Ranged Spell Attack</strong> </p><p>If this spell damages a vehicle or object that is flammable and has hit points, the object is set on fire**.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Hit:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 1d8 fire]] damage*</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*At Higher Levels:</strong> This spell's damage increases by 1d8 when you reach a total character or creature level of 5th level ([[/damage 2d8 fire]]), 11th level ([[/damage 3d8 fire]]), and 17th level ([[/damage 4d8 fire]]).</p>"
        },
